data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Excellent opportunity for a spacious, newer and nicely maintained 3BR plus Den plus Loft, 2.5BA home with a heated pool and spa, and an extended garage to accommodate oversized vehicles or a golf cart. Situated on a very private homesite in beautiful Toscana Isles, a community known for its large recreational lakes, this airy and open floor plan offers high ceilings (over 11 feet), a roomy kitchen, dinette, great room, a first-floor owner's suite with two walk-in closets, soaking tub, walk-in shower, dual vanities, and makeup counter, and a large first floor Den with French doors at the front of the home that can be used as a formal office, formal dining room, or den. The designer finishes include natural colored tile on the diagonal throughout the main living areas including the den, luxury vinyl flooring in the owner's suite, raised panel cabinets, high-end granite counter tops, beadboard finishes on the large center island and powder room, designer backsplash, stainless steel appliances, 42" cabinets with under and over cabinet lighting, 8-foot doors throughout, large baseboards, shiplap walls, and more. The large secondary bedrooms located upstairs allow for privacy for your guests and family. The airy loft/bonus room can serve as a game room or as an additional den or office for those needing two offices. The garage has an epoxy finished floor and was extended to 29 feet, allowing for additional storage, large vehicles, or a golf cart. The sizable lanai and pool/spa area offer excellent privacy with lush and mature greenery all around, making you feel like you are living on a private, tropical estate, yet you are close to everything. The community resort-style clubhouse, infinity-edge, beach-entry pool, gym, tennis/pickleball courts, playground, and dog park are easily accessible and just a short walk away. Kayak, canoe, or fish on 200 acres of interconnected lakes within the community, or participate in the many community activities. Toscana Isles is a gated community that is located only 6 miles from beautiful Suncoast Beaches, and it offers an excellent school district, as well as easy access to shopping, health care facilities including Sarasota Memorial Hospital Venice Campus, and I-75. Call today for a private showing.
